## 2026-04-03 - AnalyticsPanel duplicate color auto-suggest canonical
- Added `aliasRefCounts` (IIFE computing how many tokens reference each path as `{alias}`) and `suggestedCanonicals` (IIFE picking best canonical per hex group: most alias refs → most Figma usage → fewest path segments → alphabetical). Added `handleApplyAllSuggestions` handler to bulk-apply suggestions. Per-group UI: shows "suggested" badge on the auto-recommended token when it differs from current canonical, plus a "Use suggestion" button in the group header. Bulk UI: adds "Use all suggestions" button below "Promote all" when any group's canonical differs from its suggestion.
